node.title: A Charlie Brown Thanksgiving
node.plot: Peppermint Patty invites herself and her friends over to Charlie Brown's for Thanksgiving, and with Linus, Snoopy, and Woodstock, he attempts to throw together a Thanksgiving dinner.

node.title: Holt
node.plot: On the 17th of December 1967, Australia's Prime Minister, Harold Holt, disappeared without a trace - but not originally. Someone wants the Prime Minister dead and only time travel will allow it.
